{"tid":2196662,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《刺客教條：維京紀元》確定將提早上市和 Xbox 新主機一起在 11 月 10 日發售","createTime":"2020-09-10T05:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T08:59:56.000Z","uid":33359,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"444138da8dd4c7547f67455cb6db933805fadd2e","tid":2196662,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:29:30.000Z","msg":"在微軟徹底公開了新一代 Xbox 的上市資訊後，作為主要遊戲開發方之一的 Ubisoft 也正式宣佈，旗下今年最重要的作品《刺客教條：維京紀元》將會提早到 11 月 10 日跟新 Xbox 同一天發售。和原定的 11 月 17 日相比，這個日期提前了 7 天。也就是說 Ubisoft 原本給遊戲上架時間留出的彈性其實比較充足，是否要調整很大程度上就看微軟和 Sony 的新主機選哪一天了。（所以 PS5 如果更早賣的話，《維京紀元》會不會再提前一次？）<br />\n<br />\n除了次世代主機以外，《刺客教條：維京紀元》也已確定會登陸 PC 和 Google Stadia 平台。「我們很高興地宣佈玩家們能比預期更早地投入《刺客教條：維京紀元》的世界。」製作人 Julien Laferri&egrave;re 在聲明中這麼寫道，「我們已經迫不及待想要看到自己過去三年內打造出來的東西在所有平台上煥發生機了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巨硬今次落重本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要頂撚死罪大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f435bf013d448b80bb13ff627e4ac4dd9064fcfd","tid":2196662,"uid":255926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OrWa91CfXtY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOrWa91CfXtY&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=9c4d231a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OrWa91CfXtY</a><br />\n睇佢教你玩"},{"pid":"2cd6a4e9cdf091aaebee92b3f7acac3228c9e460","tid":2196662,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"刺客師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63be0344246dfa3f7ed18c34650a9a0289556bbd","tid":2196662,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"維京師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caaa1958c5b969eabb885d870dda523f942575ee","tid":2196662,"uid":64522,"like":1,"di